TITLE: Basic Excalidraw Component Implementation
DESCRIPTION: A simple React component example showing how to implement the Excalidraw drawing interface with minimal configuration. The component is rendered within a container with a fixed height.
SOURCE: https://github.com/excalidraw/excalidraw/blob/master/dev-docs/docs/@excalidraw/excalidraw/integration.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
function App() {
  return (
    <>
      <h1 style={{ textAlign: "center" }}>Excalidraw Example</h1>
      <div style={{ height: "500px" }}>
        <Excalidraw />
      </div>
    </>
  );
}
```

