TITLE: Dynamic Import of Excalidraw in Next.js
DESCRIPTION: Implementation using Next.js dynamic import to load the Excalidraw component only on the client side, since it doesn't support server-side rendering. This approach works specifically for importing the named Excalidraw component.
SOURCE: https://github.com/excalidraw/excalidraw/blob/master/dev-docs/docs/@excalidraw/excalidraw/integration.mdx#2025-04-17_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: jsx
