TITLE: Migrating from commitToHistory to captureUpdate in updateScene API
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to migrate from the deprecated commitToHistory parameter to the new captureUpdate parameter in the updateScene API. This change is part of the multiplayer undo/redo functionality implementation.
SOURCE: https://github.com/excalidraw/excalidraw/blob/master/packages/excalidraw/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-17_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
// before
updateScene({ elements, appState, commitToHistory: true }); // A
updateScene({ elements, appState, commitToHistory: false }); // B

// after
import { CaptureUpdateAction } from "@excalidraw/excalidraw";
updateScene({
  elements,
  appState,
  captureUpdate: CaptureUpdateAction.IMMEDIATELY,
}); // A
updateScene({
  elements,
  appState,
  captureUpdate: CaptureUpdateAction.NEVER,
}); // B
```

